-------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------- PROTOCOL SPECIFICATIONS --------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Nomencalture :
	* Text to Speech Server : TTSS
	* Text to Speech Client : TTSC
	* Media Control Socket  : MSC
	* Data Transfer Socket  : DTS


		MSC (accept) <------------ (request) MSC
	i)  TTSS                                        TTSC
	        DTS (accept) <------------ (request) DTS

	

		MSC          --data size-->          MSC
	ii) TTSS                                        TTSC
		DTS                                  DTS 


		 MSC                                 MSC
	iii) TTSS                                       TTSC
		 DTS         ---- data ---->         DTS
